manifestNotFound.comment: {Locked}Error to show when the manifest for a component id is not found.

extensionInitFailure.comment:
{Locked}Error to show when the extension failed to initialize.
    {0} is the component id for the extension.
extensionInitFailure.value: Extension failed to initialize for componentId "{0}".

extensionLoadFailure.comment: {Locked}Error to show when the extension for a component id is not found.
extensionLoadFailure.value: Extension failed to load for componentId "{0}".

expectingBaseExtension.comment: {Locked}Error to show when the loaded class does not extend BaseExtension.
expectingBaseExtension.value: Expecting a class that extends BaseExtension.

wrongExtensionType.comment: {Locked}Error to show when the loaded class does not extend the type expected by manifest.
